### Context

This data is just a smaller version of the main data since the aforementioned is a huge dataset.
Refer to https://www.kaggle.com/moltean/fruits


### Content

The following fruits and are included:
Pineapple (369 images), Pineapple Mini (450 images), Raspberry (420 images), Redcurrant (492 images), Strawberry (450 images), Strawberry Wedge (496 images).


### License

The data is open-licensed, under CC0: Public Domain, and can be used for analysis.
Refer to https://www.kaggle.com/moltean/fruits for citing the original data.


### Challenge

Detection and classification between closely related image classes with high accuracy and evaluation parameters.
